:0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"手動轉【白宮聯署 - 更新 09.09.2019 】<br />\n當我知道尋晚「最喜愛香港小姐」嘅投票數係 176 萬，我有啲想喊。<br />\n<br />\n1/ 每個聯署簽一個好嘞。簽完記得MARK返自己簽過。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 簽署＞等電郵＞確認簽署＞叫十個朋友簽<br />\n<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民（最後兩天）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/send-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsend-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e808f500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/send-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug</a><br />\n<br />\n香港政府及警察策動831太子恐怖襲擊，請美國予以制裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=d483b5a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831</a><br />\n-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests"},{"pid":"f0934890fae0a7233417367b0d7d44537fb64e1f","tid":1554974,"uid":121508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ee0d4cdc942015196d39feda43362c7ed492f06","tid":1554974,"uid":121508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:36:01.000Z","msg":"最近連登不斷出現指責、抱怨、甚至指名道姓針對個別組織。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地想步雨傘後塵？</span><br />\n<br />\n當初既場運動致勝既